                    _t('Weighing Conflicting Evidence', 'When sources conflict, advanced writers explain why they are giving more weight to one source than another — based on evidence quality, sample size, methodology, recency, and source credibility.', 'Simply citing conflicting sources without explaining how you weigh them leaves the argument unresolved.', 'Practice: given two conflicting sources, write a paragraph that explains which you find more credible and why.'),
